/ iPhone / iMac /ipad iPod touch  ,真正去到邊玩到邊<br />\n<br />\n見唔見Apple個tv app 將唔同公司串流煲劇嘅進度統一晒落去tv app?<br />\n因為每間公司都有自己嘅獨家劇, tv app 將佢哋集中晒係同一個地方以後睇睇下睇咗第二套你就唔使再逐個app開返嚟搵返邊個位邊套劇煲到第幾季第幾集!<br />\n而且更會根據你嘅買片租片煲劇嘅喜好進而推介更多正嘢俾你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzVZSsR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzVZSsR.jpg&h=2eeba650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hnRVqNT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhnRVqNT.jpg&h=80d3ebd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gh215NU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgh215NU.jpg&h=7ce4c80e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b416b11b46b9e2d735c7681ce8c5bf93494a77ba","tid":1384943,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"樓上巴打係咪住外國?<br />\n因為見你有啲 Apple TV apps<br />\nHK store 係無得 download"},{"pid":"a0c17d3521fb0621ffe2c34c02d9fc32d3ea0e32","tid":1384943,"uid":146465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b416b11b46b9e2d735c7681ce8c5bf93494a77ba","tid":1384943,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"樓上巴打係咪住外國?<br />\n因為見你有啲 Apple TV apps<br />\nHK store 係無得 download"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"update tvOS 就有<br />\n你會發現無左電影個app"},{"pid":"f231d8afa3b48b4006f0599e3a5e38ccc1110d5d","tid":1384943,"uid":127244,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b416b11b46b9e2d735c7681ce8c5bf93494a77ba","tid":1384943,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"樓上巴打係咪住外國?<br />\n因為見你有啲 Apple TV apps<br />\nHK store 係無得 download"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"唔係, 我純粹係用緊us account, <br />\n影視娛樂方便完全係兩個世界建議你都盡早轉過去 ( payment method 方便用AE 就得) <br />\n再用getflix 打通成個wifi network 咁成間屋